1. Moja najbolja drugarica *je* otišla na putovanje. (My best friend *has* gone on a trip.)
2. Prošle nedelje sam se družila sa drugaricama *iz* osnovne škole. (Last week I hung out with friends *from* elementary school.)
3. Ona je jedna od mojih najboljih drugarica *od* detinjstva. (She is one of my best friends *since* childhood.)
4. Njene drugarice *su* vrlo prijatne. (Her friends *are* very nice.)
5. Kada sam bila mladja, imala sam mnogo drugarica *koje* su se bavile baletom. (When I was younger, I had many friends *who* were involved in ballet.)
6. Moje drugarice *su* me iznenadile za moj rodjendan. (My friends *surprised* me for my birthday.)
7. Ona i ja smo već *godinama* dobre drugarice. (She and I have been good friends *for years*.)
8. Nekada smo bile vrlo *bliske* drugarice, ali smo se razdvojile kada smo krenule na fakultete. (We used to be very *close* friends, but we drifted apart when we went to college.)
9. Jedna od njenih drugarica *je* želela da se upozna sa mnom. (One of her friends *wanted* to meet me.)
10. Kada su bile u srednjoj školi, bile su najbolje drugarice *na* svetu. (When they were in high school, they were the best friends *in* the world.)